{"tid":1546913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[831太子恐襲] 我覺得唔單止要攞月台CCTV","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:50:38.000Z","uid":154808,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"212dab1c4a8170ac639d31f18aa83a20f7542ae9","tid":1546913,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"大家好似忽略左<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行車記錄，同埋其他既CCTV</span></strong>，以下係小弟既推斷:<br />\n<br />\n當日冇救護員即時入去太子月台站，淨係消防入左去，點錯數，等等跡象，就可以推斷有示威者當場被打死，詳情連登有好多post都證明到，呢度唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n入正題，如果有人當場死左，<span style=\"color: red;\">代表唔會送入醫院，直送公眾殮房</span>，咁2個問題就黎喇，用咩交通工具？同埋送去邊個公眾殮房？<br />\n<br />\n第一個答案，最直接既方法一定係用港鐵運狗+運屍體，但係，佢冇可能光明正大地，係其他地鐵站抬d屍體出黎，咁可以去邊又唔比市民發現？<span style=\"color: red;\">唯一解釋係入車廠</span>，(排除港鐵站有其他秘道)，睇返MTR Track Diagram，最近太子站有兩個車廠，1. 九龍灣車廠 2. 荃灣車廠<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4n4Yjn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4n4Yjn0.png&h=ad39d2af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個答案，邊個公眾殮房，上一上google map搵下，就見有4個公眾殮房，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zU4JvwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzU4JvwG.png&h=6bdb8d5d&s={SIZE}\" />，而最近車廠既殮房就係<span style=\"color: red;\">葵涌公眾殮房，係荃灣車廠附近</span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我假設用港鐵運送同匿藏屍體，我可以排除去九龍公眾殮房既可能性，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為紅磡冇車廠呢個條件去匿藏作進一步部署</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我個結論係，太子站打死人&gt;封站&gt;運屍體入荃灣車廠&gt;葵涌公眾殮房&gt;部署&gt;去唔同地方製造自殺/被殺既現象<br />\n<br />\n我認為可以攞港鐵入荃灣車廠既行車紀錄，荃灣車廠既CCTV，葵涌公眾殮房既CCTV<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，以上都係純粹推測"},{"pid":"56f83ea6a4f988bc42276cb1648690396125ea45","tid":1546913,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 終極文宣 對準政權 全民抗共</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界 全世界一齊印！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbdefb198b4fff89a0e0dade722a7e7b64441df3","tid":1546913,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"3ba338bd08e45b2729fd25fde60429b706ee0f35","tid":1546913,"uid":154808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"e494637998b694fe894c659b96fead3b6a7cc360","tid":1546913,"uid":220723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{